Hello,
My name is Master Ahmed Q. I am 17 years old. I write to solicit for your
partnership in claiming {US$8Million} in a financial bank. The Fund
{US$8Million} was my late father's share from the (Over-invoiced) Gold deal
with Tuvalu Government within 2014. However, I don’t want my government to
know about the funds and the 13 kilos Gold deposit. If this proposal
interests you, let me know by sending me an email and I will send to you
detailed Information on how this transaction would be successfully
transacted. So I am compelled to ask that you will stand on my behalf and
receive this fund and the gold into any account that is solely controlled
by you. I will compensate you with 50% of the total amount involved as
gratification for being my partner in the transfer.
Sincerely,
Ahmed
